a\bmod{n}= a - \left\lfloor \frac{a}{n} \right\rfloor \times n
a \in \mathbb{Z}
kn + b
k, b \in \mathbb{Z}
0 \leq b < n
 a = b 
n
 nk + b - n\left\lfloor \frac{kn + b}{n}\right\rfloor = nk + b + n\left\lfloor k + \frac{b}{n}\right\rfloor 
\frac{b}{n} < 1
b < n
nk + b - n\lfloor k \rfloor = nk + b - nk = b
